data.schema-format#Schema Format:
Forms are defined as JSON schemas:
{
  "title": "Contact Form",
  "fields": [
    { "type": "text", "name": "fullName", "label": "Full Name", "required": true },
    { "type": "email", "name": "email", "label": "Email" },
    { "type": "select", "name": "department", "label": "Department",
      "options": ["Engineering", "Sales", "Support"] },
    { "type": "textarea", "name": "message", "label": "Message" }
  ]
}

data.conditional-logic#Conditional Logic:
Show or hide fields based on other field values:
{
  "type": "text",
  "name": "otherReason",
  "label": "Please specify",
  "condition": { "field": "reason", "eq": "other" }
}

data.shared-patterns#Shared Patterns:
All X Suite packages follow consistent conventions:
Theme-aware — Inherit from the global ThemeProvider
Composable — Combine packages freely within layouts
Server-side ready — Support SSR and hydration patterns
Type-safe — Full TypeScript generics for data models
import { DataGrid } from '@mfe/x-data-grid';
import { BarChart } from '@mfe/x-charts';
function Dashboard({ data }) {
  return (
    <>
      <BarChart data={data} xField="month" yField="revenue" />
      <DataGrid rows={data} variant="compact" />
    </>
  );
}

