data.resource-scheduling#Resource Scheduling:
Assign events to resources (rooms, people, equipment):
<Scheduler
  view="timeline"
  resources={[
    { id: 'room-a', title: 'Conference Room A' },
    { id: 'room-b', title: 'Conference Room B' },
  ]}
  events={bookings}
/>

data.recurring-events#Recurring Events:
Use the built-in recurrence editor for repeating events:
<RecurrenceEditor
  value={rrule}
  onChange={setRrule}
  maxOccurrences={52}
/>

data.quick-start#Quick Start:
import { KanbanBoard } from '@mfe/x-kanban';
<KanbanBoard
  columns={['Backlog', 'In Progress', 'Review', 'Done']}
  items={tasks}
